data.description: Seller Ready to Move - MAKE AN OFFER -  The home has a Lake Murray view in Sunset Bay where the subdivision has a private boat ramp, dock, picnic pavilion area, firepit, kayak rack and sandy beach, all directly across from this beautiful home. This 3/2.5 home built in 2015 has an expansive great room, kitchen, dining room combination with fireplace, built-in stainless appliances, gas stove, pantry closet and mudroom and half bath leading to the 2 car garage. Built-in vaccuum system helps keep the hardwood floors down and carpet upstairs clean. The upstairs Jack and Jill full bath is between 2 bedrooms and the large master suite with a deck overlooking Lake Murray and separate shower, garden tub, water closet and dual sinks is an owner's dream bedroom. The home is only a 10 minute drive to the Hwy 1/378 split in Lexington. Neighborhood visitor parking is across the street too. The beautiful lake view pictures don't do it justice so come take a look for yourself.
